parameters:
This is a monument dedicated to the moon god who governs the
love of lovers. It is said that if you offer a prayer, you
will be united with your beloved.

events.name: ◆１　宿で一泊。ライアンイベまで

parameters:
Oh my... There's an inn in a place like this, huh? \SE[0]
Are we going to rest here today?
You've worked so hard. Good job... Good job...

This hotel is called The Path to Ulyssean. \!\SM[nod]\SE[15]
Hehe... It's surprisingly stylish.
\SE[2]Hotel...? Um, is it different from a regular inn?

Eh...! Y-Yes, that's right... It's probably not that
different...? Um, maybe...
困っているようなふきだしアイコンを。
キャラはハタヤキ村の生き残りの勇者役の子。
強制イベでいい気がする。

\SM[nod]\SE[31] Hmm... It's such nice weather... \SE[1] It
feels good to be able to sleep in bed after a long time.
\SE[0] How about you, Laura? Did you sleep well?

\SE[21]Maybe it's because I relaxed in the bath?
\!\SE[21]I was able to sleep really well.

\SE[50] (I feel like I just fainted because of Luna... but
it's just a feeling...)

\SM[tremble]\SE[51] (Ugh... Now that I remember, I'm
starting to feel embarrassed...)

\SE[4]Laura! You too...! \SE[33]Thanks to you, we were able
to escape from the village somehow...

\SE[3]... Huh? \SE[5] Weren't you with Rebecca? \SE[3]
Are you in the bathroom now?

\SE[7]...Oh, I see! \.So you're the one who's been through a
lot...! \!\SE[14]Rebecca was kidnapped by a bad guy!
\SE[13]...Can you tell me more about it?

\SE[9]We managed to escape somehow... \!\SE[8]But then we
got caught by another group of guys...

\SE[7]I think those guys are child kidnappers....
\SE[37]There are rumors among the people around here that
there are people who kidnap children and sell them.

\SE[12]Do you know anything about the place where those
people went?

\SE[12]What I heard is... that they seem to be gathering at
the Mottrel Mine ahead... \!\SE[38]Sorry, I don't know
anything more than that...

\SE[0]Don't worry. I feel the same way as you.
\!\SE[14]Let's save Rebecca together.

\SE[14]In that case, we'll figure something out....
\SE[13]Will you wait here? \SE[0]Don't worry. I'll
definitely bring Rebecca- chan back with me.
一旦会話〆　クエスト発生
The road to Hotel Ulyssean... The best night awaits you.
By the way, is... Laura an acquaintance of yours?

\SE[2]I'm Lunaroa. \SE[2]I've even changed your diapers
before... But I guess you've forgotten about that a long
time ago.

\SM[tremble]Y-Yeah, please stop! Spare me... It's
embarrassing...
